 Epoch  Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch Epoch def img_detector(img_path):
    img = cv2.imread(img_path)
    cv_rgb = cv2.cvtColor(img, cv2.COLOR_BGR2RGB)
    plt.imshow(cv_rgb)
    plt.show()
    if dog_detector(img_path):
        print('Hi, dog! I guess you are a {}!'.format(Xception_predict_breed(img_path)))
        print("--"*25)
    elif face_detector(img_path):
        print('Hello, human! You look like a {}!'.format(Xception_predict_breed(img_path)))
        print("--"*25)
    else:
        print("Error!")
        print("--"*25)
